User <%=h @sender.login %>, the current admin of group '<%=h @group.title %>', is tired of doing the administration.
He asks you to become the new admin of that group.

	You can accept or decline the invitation here:
	<%= "http://#{SITE_URL}" + myinvitations_path(@reciever) %>
	(All your pending invitations are shown there)
	
	
	View the group profile:
	<%= "http://#{SITE_URL}" + group_path(@group) %>
	
	View the profile of the user who invited you:
	<%= "http://#{SITE_URL}" + user_path(@sender) %>